==預後==
皮質壞死是一種嚴重的危及生命的病症，且死亡率超過50％。<!--Those mortality rates are even higher in neonates with the condition due to the overall difficult nature of neonatal care and an increased frequency of comorbid conditions.  The extent of the necrosis is a major determinant of the prognosis, which in turn is dependent on the duration of [[ischemia|ischemia]], duration of [[oliguria|oliguria]], and the severity of the precipitating conditions. Of those that survive the initial event, there are varying degrees of recovery possible, depending on the extent of the damage.-->

